data.description: Welcome to this stunning SWM & Sons custom built acreage home in the highly sought-after Choctaw community.  This home offers the perfect blend of elegance and functionality.  You will be greeted by an open floor plan that creates a seamless flow throughout the home.  All the rooms are spacious which provides plenty of private space for everyone to enjoy.  Attention to detail is evident with the beautiful crown moldings and custom wood features.  One of the highlights of this property is its outdoor oasis.  Imagine relaxing in your own backyard retreat, complete with water feature and waterfall, and a green house for those with a green thumb.  The storm shelter provides peace of mind during inclement weather, while the sprinkler system helps keep your lawn looking lush and vibrant.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own.  Seller to provide a $1,500.00 flooring allowance.
